    "en": {
      "name": "Number 39: Utopia the Envoy of Light",
      "effect": "2 Level 4 monsters\nCannot be destroyed by battle, except with a \"Number\" monster. (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 monster you control; the first time it would be destroyed by battle or card effect this turn, it is not destroyed. When the second attack of this turn is declared: You can make this card gain 2500 ATK, and if you do, it gains this effect.\n\u25cf When this card destroys a monster by battle and sends it to the GY: You can Special Summon it to your field.",
      "official": false
    },
